The Romanian utility  Apa Prod SA  is
waiting for bids on water and sewage network upgrades in the
western county of Hunedoara under a contract estimated at 36.7
million lei ($11 million).  The utility is seeking bids by May 20 for the improvements
in the towns of Calan and Hateg, according to a  procurement
